    {
      "id": "t31",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.text-align-center > div.max-width-large > h1.heading-style-h1",
      "en": "Creating Value the Right Way — Our Path to Responsible Oleochemicals",
      "cn": "以正道创造价值——我们的负责任油脂化学之路"
    },
    {
      "id": "t32",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.layout6_content-left > div.margin-bottom > h2.heading-style-h3",
      "en": "What is Oleochemicals",
      "cn": "什么是油脂化学"
    },
    {
      "id": "t33",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.layout6_content-left > div.margin-bottom > p.text-size-medium",
      "en": "Oleochemicals, derived from natural oils and fats including palm, coconut and animal sources, provide an alternative to petroleum-based products.",
      "cn": "油脂化学产品源自天然油脂，包括棕榈油、椰子油及动物油脂，是石油基产品的可持续替代选择。"
    },
    {
      "id": "t34",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.layout6_content-left > div.margin-bottom > p.text-size-medium",
      "en": "These compounds serve as key ingredients in soaps, detergents, cosmetics, pharmaceuticals and various industrial applications. Responsibly sourced oleochemicals represent a sustainable substitute for conventional petrochemicals.",
      "cn": "这些化合物是肥皂、洗涤剂、化妆品、医药与各类工业应用的关键成分。负责任采购的油脂化学产品是传统石化产品的可持续替代方案。"
    },
    {
      "id": "t35",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.layout6_text-wrapper > div.margin-bottom > h3.heading-style-h6",
      "en": "How we source",
      "cn": "我们如何采购"
    },
    {
      "id": "t36",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.w-layout-grid > div.layout6_text-wrapper > p",
      "en": "We select feedstocks with care and accountability.",
      "cn": "我们以审慎与责任感挑选原料。"
    },
    {
      "id": "t37",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.layout6_text-wrapper > div.margin-bottom > h3.heading-style-h6",
      "en": "How we operate",
      "cn": "我们如何运营"
    },
    {
      "id": "t38",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.w-layout-grid > div.layout6_text-wrapper > p",
      "en": "We measure results and answers for them daily.",
      "cn": "我们每日衡量成果，并对成果负责。"
    },
    {
      "id": "t39",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.layout353_content-left > div.margin-bottom > h2.heading-style-h2",
      "en": "Pillars of Sustainability",
      "cn": "可持续发展支柱"
    },
    {
      "id": "t40",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.w-layout-grid > div.layout353_content-left > p.text-size-medium",
      "en": "Aligning with IOI Group's Sustainability Policy, the IOI Oleochemical Division commits to sustainable operations across all sites through initiatives aligned with the United Nations Sustainable Development Goals.",
      "cn": "IOI Oleochemical 事业部与 IOI 集团的可持续发展政策保持一致，承诺通过呼应联合国可持续发展目标的举措，在所有厂区推行可持续运营。"
    },
    {
