      "context": "div#w-node-_92c54fed-5da1-0a54-c3b8-a3910d9e9702-6a894c88 > div.layout353_content-item > p",
      "en": "Optimize natural resource utilization and reduce environmental impact through the implementation of sustainable processes and the development of environmentally responsible products.",
      "cn": "通过实施可持续工艺与开发环境友善产品，优化自然资源利用，降低环境影响。"
    },
